@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Make Payment (Prototype)

' =========================================================
' TEXT DESCRIPTION (Steps map to actions)
' Step 1  System shows payment screen for a PENDING booking.
' Step 2  Renter enters payment details.
' Step 3  Renter confirms payment.
' Step 4  System processes payment (prototype).
' Step 5  If failed, system shows failure and renter retries or cancels (end).
' Step 6  If success, system marks payment SUCCESS.
' Step 7  System updates booking to CONFIRMED.
' Step 8  System shows receipt/confirmation (end).
' =========================================================

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam DefaultFontSize 16
skinparam ArrowFontSize 14
skinparam nodesep 30
skinparam ranksep 30

|System|
start
:1. Show payment screen;

|Renter|
:2. Enter payment details;
:3. Confirm payment;

|System|
:4. Process payment (prototype);

if (Payment successful?) then (Yes)
  :6. Mark payment SUCCESS;
  :7. Set booking CONFIRMED;
  :8. Show receipt/confirmation;
  stop
else (No)
  :5. Show payment failed;
  |Renter|
  if (Retry?) then (Yes)
    :5. Retry payment later;
    stop
  else (No)
    :5. Cancel payment;
    stop
  endif
endif

@enduml